data.description:
Seize the extraordinary opportunity to own and develop a sprawling half-acre corner lot nestled in the heart of downtown Delray, a mere stone's throw from the serene waterfront. This exceptional property, strategically positioned across the street from the lush Merritt Park, and just three blocks from the vibrant Atlantic Avenue, the NEW Sunday Village, local library, and renowned tennis stadium, presents an unparalleled canvas for developers with a vision. The property's substantial size and prime location offer a rare chance to subdivide into 3 or 4 distinct lots, each serving as a foundation for modern, single-family homes tailored to the sophisticated tastes of today's discerning homeowners. Imagine crafting a collection of homes where cutting-edge design meets the tranquility of nature, all within the dynamic setting of downtown Delray Beach.

For developers poised to make a mark in Delray's coveted real estate landscape, this property is more than just land; it's a canvas for creativity, a gateway to luxury living, and a unique opportunity to shape the future of upscale urban living. Don't miss your chance to transform this once-in-a-generation offering into a breathtaking enclave of architectural excellence and unparalleled lifestyle.
